name: Exstinctio
description:
Annihilation is an eternal struggle between two parts of the soul in one person. One part is looking for an opening to the sky and eternity, the other one is eager to grab onto the ground and is ready to jump. One removes the protection and opens up to the light, the other puts on a mask and passionately longs for explosion.

Who is that great judge who will tell them to fight, who is that great sage who will tell them to break?

There's only one thing that is known. If one of them wins, the game will be over for everyone.
